Mon Mar  3 14:25:52 2003  Thomas Roessler  <roessler@does-not-exist.org>

	* /cvs/mutt/mutt/ChangeLog: # changelog commit

	* /cvs/mutt/mutt/copy.c, /cvs/mutt/mutt/sort.c:
