Wed Nov 13 10:10:52 2002  Thomas Roessler  <roessler@does-not-exist.org>

	* /cvs/mutt/mutt/main.c:
	From: Thomas Roessler <roessler@does-not-exist.org>

	A description of -A was lacking from the help string.

