	* hook.c:
	Avoid excessive unhooking from within hooks.  Problem noted by
	Eugene Lee <eugene@anime.net> on mutt-users.

	* doc/Makefile.in:
	Don't rely on GNU make's implicit rules for shell scripts.  Noted by
	EGE.

