	* doc/mutt.man: Remove some unnecessary spaces.

	* doc/mutt.man, main.c:
	Fix usage information.  Noted by Mikko Hänninen.

	* acconfig.h, configure.in, globals.h:
	Check volatility of sig_atomic_t.

