Wed Sep  1 21:41:19 1999  Thomas Roessler  <roessler@guug.de>

	* doc/Makefile.in, Makefile.am:
	A couple of build process and portability fixes concerning the
	automatically generated documentation.

	* mutt.h, init.c:
